experiment Next1800
instrument HEA
start 2014 11 24 1100
end 2014 11 24 1400
status R
description The next 1800 ms of ionospheric HF-modification by EISCAT Heating
contact Björn Gustavsson
phone +4777645668
email bjorn.gustavsson@uit.no
operator Bjorn Gustavsson
submitter Björn Gustavsson
resources PP(18),NO(9)
notes
Experiment to study the transition from Langmuir-turbulence that dominates
HF-modification just after HF-on to the UH-effects that has a slower growth.
This experiment requires quiet ionospheric conditions and EISCAT Heating and the
UHF and VHF radars simultaneously.
